197
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:35,480
I brought the remaining
nine kits I tested on.

198
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:35,970
Would you like to take a look?

199
00:07:36,090 --> 00:07:37,570
No. It's fine.

200
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,400
