288
00:11:10,450 --> 00:11:11,570
Calm down.

289
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,930
Listen to me.

290
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,690
Come here. Take a seat.

291
00:11:15,930 --> 00:11:16,410
Come over here.

292
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:19,120
Sit.

293
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,410
Think about it logically.

294
